              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {
                "11": {
                  "id": "11",
                  "speaker": "Valeria",
                  "text": "To answer your deeply hurtful query - I am an investigator. THE investigator. Valeria, Sleuth of Helm. Pleasure to meet you.",
